para_trans: Government Decision Number: AIT-9225 / Q. No.18 / MATS
The functions of the Task Force shall be as follows: -
1) An AI policy has been prepared in the state of Maharashtra in line with the India AI Mission policy adoption.
Will make appropriate recommendations, including the following.
a) AI Charter, creating goals for the state.
b) Skill development, capacity building.
a) To attract investments by companies in the AI sector in Maharashtra.
d) AI computing capabilities, datasets, data protection security measures.
e) To promote AI-based research and educational activities.
e) AI-based capacity building in the public and private sectors.
e) Effective implementation of AI strategy in the industry and startups programme.
2) According to the above procedure, the task force should submit recommendations to the government within 3 months.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
